+## Overview
+
+The dataset contains 30 orders totaling $7,154.44 in revenue. The average order is worth $238.48, and the median order value is $204.94.
+
+## Top Products
+
+Gadget leads with $2,392.00 in revenue, followed by Widget at $2,118.94. Doohickey contributes $1,513.00, while Sprocket trails at $1,130.50. The top two products account for about 63% of total revenue.
+
+## Regional Performance
+
+North is the strongest region with $2,176.35, followed by East at $1,830.79 and South at $1,732.48. West lags at $1,414.82, roughly 20% of total revenue and the weakest of the four regions.
+
+## Recommendations
+
+- Focus sales effort on the West region, which trails North by about $761.
+- Promote Gadget and Widget together, since they drive most revenue.
+- Review Sprocket pricing or demand, as it contributes the least revenue.
